See that intervals within 2015-09-24 (that's single segment) are filled properly, but subsequent intervals in between two segments are not.
I'd say that this _is_ indeed confusing. Well, I got confused, too.

With this working as is, we'd have to do the filling client side, as our processing expects that result of a single query will be continuous. I'd rather have that done Druid side.

Anyway, thanks @CHOIJAEHONG1 for clarifying what's going on here.
